@jeenbroekstra
The whole wrapped connection approach here makes it hard for me to add support for transaction settings. The problem is that code higher up will often override the begin() and begin(IsolationLevel level) methods to hook into the transaction handling approach. With the new begin(TransactionSetting[] settings) simply calling wrapped.begin(settings) the code higher up will have to override the new begin method in order to fully hook into the transaction flow.
I'm not sure right now how to fix this. I was initially hoping to hook in like I did in the AbstractSailConnection.

